spec_data.Name: mash
spec_data.Description:
mash is a tool that queries a koji buildsystem for the latest RPMs for
any particular tag, and creates repositories of those RPMs, including
any multlib RPMs that are necessary.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 06:08:00 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Koji buildsystem to yum repository converter
